For each i (1 â‰¤ i â‰¤ Î›(Î¶)), there exists a unique m such that (i, C:sub:L(m)) âˆˆ C:sub:Î¶. (Each word index is assigned one category).
For each i, if (i, Î±) âˆˆ W:sub:Î¶ and (i, C:sub:L(m)) âˆˆ C:sub:Î¶, then Î± âˆˆ C:sub:L(m) (The assigned category is valid for the word at that index).
